2026-07-16  Alexander I.Grafov  <grafov@inet.name>

	Version 0.4.0

	* config/config.go, cmd/adgui/main.go: config file created automatically
	  on first launch with localized defaults and commented keys.
	* config/config.go: environment variables now take priority over config
	  values; code defaults used when neither is set
	  (ADGUARD_CMD, ADGUARD_KILL_CMD, ADGUARD_SUDO_WRAP, ADGUARD_SUDO_ASKPASS).
	* README.md, README.ru.md, README.eo.md: updated highlights section with
	  feature summary and native GUI description.

2026-07-15  Alexander I.Grafov  <grafov@inet.name>

	Version 0.3.0

	* commands/sudowrap/sudowrap.go, ui/sudo_prompt.go: when TUN mode
	  requires root, adgui now injects an isolated sudo wrapper with askpass
	  support (ADGUARD_SUDO_ASKPASS=1); password stored in .pass (mode 0600)
	  and wiped on exit; falls back to sudo -n when no ticket is cached.
	* commands/sudowrap/sudowrap.go: added ADGUARD_SUDO_ASKPASS config key to
	  disable the password dialog entirely (keep only sudo -n).
	* ui/ui.go: added quit confirmation dialog to prevent accidental exit.
	* res/adguardvpn-gui.svg: added project logo and embedded in README files.
	* README.eo.md, README.ru.md: added Esperanto and Russian translations.
	* All source files: added GPL license headers.
	* ui/about_panel.go: added license information and project URL.
	* README.md, README.ru.md, README.eo.md: added YouTube demo link and
	  adguardvpn-cli prerequisite note.
	* Makefile: Wayland builds now use correct build tags.
	* Makefile, adgui-run: renamed X11 references to XLibre.

2026-06-22  Alexander I.Grafov  <grafov@inet.name>

	Version 0.2.0

	* ui/ipregion_panel.go: added IP Region dashboard tab to check how GeoIP
	  databases and popular web services classify the current egress IP (IPv4
	  and IPv6); scan runs on demand via Where am I? with progress and cancel.
	* ui/ipregion_panel.go: when VPN is connected, compare selected location
	  with external checks; mismatches are marked with ! in the services table.
	* ipregion/: ported region-detection logic from Davoyan/ipregion (MIT);
	  optional API keys in ~/.config/adgui/service-keys (INI).
	* ipregion/cache.go: cache scan results under XDG cache (~/.cache/adgui)
	  per VPN state and location; show cache age on the tab and reuse on open.

2026-06-21  Alexander I.Grafov  <grafov@inet.name>

	Version 0.1.0

	* ui/i18n.go: interface localization via Fyne i18n; English, Russian,
	  and Esperanto; language follows system locale with English fallback.
	* commands/exclusions_persistence.go: site exclusion lists persist
	  automatically to ~/.config/adgui/site-exclusions/ (general.txt and
	  selective.txt) on any change; legacy ~/.local/share paths still load.
	* ui/connections_panel.go: Connect To location bookmarks with star column
	  and sort-by-bookmarks; stored in ~/.config/adgui/bookmarks with stale
	  entry pruning.
	* commands/connections_history.go: connection history for recent VPN
	  locations.
	* ui/about_panel.go: About tab with adgui and adguardvpn-cli version info.
	* ui/ui.go: import and export of domain lists via native system file
	  dialogs (.adgui plain-text format).
	* theme/flags.go: country flags in the location list (lipis/flag-icons,
	  MIT, embedded).
	* ui/command_queue.go: dashboard tab to inspect and kill stuck
	  adguardvpn-cli processes.
	* commands/commands.go: site exclusions tab (General and Selective modes),
	  domain filter, append, remove, clear, paste URLs as domain rules.
	* ui/ui.go: tray menu quick access to exclusion mode and domain lists;
	  read ~/.config/adgui/config on startup.
